{"tid":1528134,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[熱烈討論] 如果要拍一輯香港革命紀錄片……","createTime":"2019-09-01T12:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T14:23:35.000Z","uid":285988,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8804517fea8c49e636199ee8f56ee92a6c0ea5ab","tid":1528134,"uid":285988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:47:07.000Z","msg":"1. 改咩電影名/紀錄片名？<br />\n2. 如果要開拍，用咩方法向 記者/抗爭者/市民 徵集錄影片段？<br />\n3. 香港/外國 有咩 電影公司、導演 會接拍？<br />\n<br />\n我諗咗一個電影名，主要係抄Winter on Fire <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中文︰炎夏霾霧：香港自由之戰<br />\n英文︰Summer of Haze: Hong Kong's Fight for Freedom<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n和平、理性、非暴力 + 長期耐心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反對外國勢力入侵，打倒馬克思主義！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剿滅共匪，還我祖國河山！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c643615efe5b9db4de13b6cf33de06ff77fac81","tid":1528134,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:47:21.000Z","msg":"我地需要你關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[推上熱門］［92 &amp; 93］中學生為我地上前線 我地一齊聲援中學生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1527952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1527952</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0VUpjiC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0VUpjiC.jpg&h=9cea0167&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c8ec995642bde